@startuml engine-retriever
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

class Retriever {
  - _store : VectorStore
  - _embed_fn : EmbedFn
  --
  + __init__(index_dir: Path, embed_fn: EmbedFn,\n           collection_name: str = "kb")
  + search(query: str, top_k: int = 5,\n          top_n: int | None = 20,\n          threshold: float = 0.0,\n          seed: int | None = None) : list[Chunk]
}

class VectorStore {
  + query(...) : list[dict]
}

interface EmbedFn <<Callable[[str], list[float]]>>

class Chunk {
  + text : str
  + source_file : str
  + heading : str
}

class IndexNotFoundError <<exception>>

Retriever --> VectorStore : queries
Retriever --> EmbedFn : encodes query
Retriever ..> Chunk : returns list of
Retriever ..> IndexNotFoundError : raises if index_dir missing

note right of Retriever
  top_n candidates fetched from ChromaDB;
  top_k randomly sampled from them.
  seed pins RNG for test determinism.
  top_n=None → deterministic top_k.
  Raises IndexNotFoundError if
  index_dir does not exist —
  message includes rebuild instructions.
end note

@enduml
